my colleagues even followed it up with a visit to the customers. My friend Josh who wants to join his gym had a meeting yesterday and a follow-up has been scheduled for tomorrow. He&rsquo;s also writing a follow-up to the acclaimed &ldquo;the invisible man&rdquo; so he&rsquo;s so busy that he won&rsquo;t have time to pay a follow-up visit to the gym for the time being. Therefore I handed Josh the membership agreement for Jason and will follow up with him in the next couple days. Last Thursday he complained that he was treated badly at Starbucks. As a result, a barista provided a referral to a senior staff member who in turn referred his case to the manager. He&rsquo;ll follow up the case with the manager to be sure that it&rsquo;ll be dealt with seriously. In addition, he&rsquo;s been suffering from a stroke so I referred him to a cardiologist. Recently, Josh posted on an online forum and suggested building an art gallery to boost tourism which was supported by many people on the forum. They asked the forum administrator for a referral to a district councilor. They&rsquo;ll follow up with the district councilor on the matter being discussed. I&rsquo;ll follow up the issue too. His suggestions for the city&rsquo;s future and the citizens are deemed necessary...."},{"pid":"593c285bacd42711dd4a5688050890dd2bd9b8ed","tid":1477972,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2bbd1b52402679721634344a8f63e091d2f890","tid":1477972,"uid":285834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53fbcb6bc4d3443699e8df76314bdc73b87c489e","tid":1477972,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"Athlean X<br />\n不過男仔多<br />\n自己跟內容減返份量啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:21:32.000Z","msg":"想知hiit係咪好過跑步？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"係 一來時間短 做後會繼續燃燒卡路里<br />\n二來強度大 消耗卡路里更多<br />\n三來更針對全身肌肉強化 相比跑步更有效增肌"},{"pid":"082cac26863c4f2f68704af49f78bb384ce984f1","tid":1477972,"uid":7343